<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-03-0484 </DOCNO><TEXT>The paper provides an in-depth view of the energy situation and energypolicy in Japan and detailed data are included. Topics covered are: energysituation in Japan, including energy supply and demand and recent energydevelopments; energy policy of Japan, including securing stable oil supplies,promoting the development and introduction of alternative energy, promotingenergy conservation, promoting international energy cooperation and policieson coal, natural gas, electricity, nuclear energy and energy researchand development; and the Agency of Natural Resources and Energy.</TEXT></DOC>